  <lyrics>[V1]
 Suma Dios Awqui nayat amt'asitay,
 Juma sapaquiw nayatjja yatista.
 ¿Qhitirus sart'ajj? Juma sapaquítaw
 Arumay uruy nayat amt'asita.
 
[V2]
 Amigonacas armapjjetuw Tatay,
 Cunapachatejj yatipjje nayjjata.
 lyawsañajjampejj arcascaquímaw,
 Amparamat catthapisisaw sará.
 
[V3]
 Familianacajjat amt'asim Tatay,
 Chuymanacapar sapüruy amtayam.
 Juma sapaquiw chuymanacaps uñt'tajj,
 Munasiñamasti takempipanay.
 
 </lyrics></song>